<@U5Z6RM8R0> 

Hope the site is coming along nicely for you! I know your mentee hasn't been too engaging, but we still want to say that we have really appreciated having you be part of our 1st Summer E-Mentoring Pilot Study and hope you have enjoyed it too! The students have given us some incredibly *POSITIVE* feedback for all of you Rockstar E-Mentors and hugely appreciate your help!

*We now just need you to complete this quick debrief form (Link is here: <https://prospela.typeform.com/to/wPkrSE>)*

We want to hear your *HONEST* opinion about the experience. We'll be using your feedback to help us build the product in the future so don't tell us "It was great" if you didn't feel that way! 
Don't worry, you won't hurt our feelings :smiley:
